The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Saleh skipper
Dhaka: Batsman Rajin Saleh will captain Bangladesh in the next months Champions Trophy in place of the injured Habibul Bashar, the Bangladesh Cricket Board (BCB) said on Wednesday. Rajin Saleh will lead Bangladesh in the ICC Champions trophy in England in September while wicketkeeper Khaled Mashud will be his deputy, a BCB statement said.  (REUTERS)  Copyright 
